chunks.translated_text:
The Precious Light of Universal Communication Great General Lei’s Command, dispatching the Universal Vision Great General Zhu Lie.

Thirty-Six Deputy Generals:
Deputy Generals:
Marshal of All-Heaven Ghost-Seizing, Chen Xi;
Marshal of Cloud-Road Pursuit, Sun Chang;
Marshal of Heavenly Bureau Inspection, Wang Herou;
Marshal of Flying Heaven Swiftness, Xu Xun;
Marshal of Driving Away Malevolent Spirits, Zhao Chong;
Marshal of Heavenly Medicine and Healing, Zhou Hong;
Marshal of Severing Malaria and Dysentery, Zhao Gang;
Marshal of Resolving Oaths and Averting Misfortune, Wang Guoxian;
Marshal of Protecting the Afflicted, You Kuiju;
Marshal of Direct-Day Demon-Seizing, Yuan Tingchen;
Marshal of Calming Fright and Settling the Po, Feng Xiangfu;
Marshal of Expelling Demons and Dispelling Specters, Ma Shaoxin;
Marshal of Subduing Demons and Neutralizing Poison, Bu Xin;
Marshal of Resolving Spirit-Calamities, Ni Tiansun;
Marshal of Gathering Demons and Seizing Poison, Xiang Zhong;
Marshal of Eliminating Demons and Purifying Filth, Huang Gong;
Marshal of Restraining the Hun and Controlling the Po, Chu Zhen;
Marshal of Pursuing the Hun and Seizing the Po, Wei Jinfu;
Marshal of Healing Consumption and Melting Poison, Liu Shao;
Marshal of Resolving All Curses and Filth, Zhao Ping;
Marshal of Transcending Spirits and Extending Life, Xu Chuncheng;
Marshal of Dispersing Disasters and Dissolving Misfortune, Wang Jie;
Marshal of Removing Evil and Ugliness, Xu Guoqi;
Marshal of Seizing Demons and Resolving Poison, Fang Shangwen;
Marshal of Resolving Hidden Connections, Fu Yu;
Marshal of Gathering Poison and Seizing Demons, Dou Yannian;
Marshal of Resolving Tomb Litigation, Gao Xian;
Marshal of Annihilating Malevolent Spirits, Li Yi;
Marshal of Slaying Demons and Eradicating Specters, Ma Yaochen;
Marshal of Eliminating Demons and Healing Illness, Diao Hanchen;
Marshal of Pacifying the Six Spirits, Zhu Xuan;
Marshal of Middle Realm Inspection, Wen Gao;
Marshal of Earthly Realm Inspection, Xu Shen;
Marshal of All Bureaus’ Inspection, Shan Xi;
Marshal of Three Realms’ Petition and Aversion, Feng Qingnian;
Marshal of Resolving Calamity and Saving from Distress, Wang Gang.

The above thirty-six Heavenly Generals all wear felt caps and wide sleeves, vermilion shoes and long skirts. When performing rituals, they may be summoned at will. Clasp the mudra of sincere intent, recite the Great Incantation of the Heavenly Heart, and the response will be mystically communicated.

Without invitation, do not recklessly transmit this to the unworthy or those devoid of virtue. Those whose names have been memorialized at the Golden Portal may be permitted to transmit and initiate into this Dharma, but an oath must first be sworn before imparting it.

*Shangqing Tianxin Zhengfa*, Scroll Two, concludes.
*Shangqing Tianxin Zhengfa*, Scroll Three begins.
